      "span_text": "For an athlete with high levels of Past-Negative, such a situation would be plausibly built into a negative vision of the past and the self, and result in even more negative expectations toward the future: [CITATION_1] showed in a longitudinal study that elevated levels of Past-Negative may produce a negative bias in future expectations."
